<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>
<h:html xmlns:h="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:orx="http://openrosa.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2002/xforms" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:jr="http://openrosa.org/javarosa" xmlns:vellum="http://commcarehq.org/xforms/vellum">
	<h:head>
		<h:title>Stethoscope Form</h:title>
		<model>
			<instance>
				<data xmlns:jrm="http://dev.commcarehq.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://openrosa.org/formdesigner/4B8AA771-D8CD-4E27-9775-B768C19C9E78" uiVersion="1" version="1" name="Stethoscope Form">
					<What_does_this_look_like />
					<no_media />
					<has_refs />
				</data>
			</instance>
			<bind nodeset="/data/What_does_this_look_like" type="xsd:string" />
			<bind nodeset="/data/no_media" type="xsd:string" />
			<bind nodeset="/data/has_refs" type="xsd:string" />
			<itext>
				<translation lang="en" default="">
					<text id="What_does_this_look_like-label">
						<value>What does this look like?</value>
						<value form="image">jr://file/commcare/image/data/What_does_this_look_like.png</value>
					</text>
					<text id="no_media-label">
						<value>No media</value>
					</text>
					<text id="has_refs-label">
						<value>Here is a ref <output value="/data/no_media" /> with some trailing text and "bad" < xml.</value>
					</text>
				</translation>
			</itext>
		</model>
	</h:head>
	<h:body>
		<input ref="/data/What_does_this_look_like">
			<label ref="jr:itext('What_does_this_look_like-label')" />
		</input>
		<input ref="/data/no_media">
			<label ref="jr:itext('no_media-label')" />
		</input>
		<input ref="/data/has_refs">
			<label ref="jr:itext('has_refs-label')" />
		</input>
	</h:body>
</h:html>

_attachments.98458acd899b4d5f87df042a7585e8bb.xml:
<h:html xmlns:h="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:orx="http://openrosa.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2002/xforms" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:jr="http://openrosa.org/javarosa" xmlns:vellum="http://commcarehq.org/xforms/vellum">
	<h:head>
		<h:title>Remove Point</h:title>
		<model>
			<instance>
				<data xmlns:jrm="http://dev.commcarehq.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://openrosa.org/formdesigner/BA9737A1-94A8-4CB0-B3AD-3EA187328CC7" uiVersion="1" version="1" name="Remove Point">
					<confirm_remove/>
				</data>
			</instance>
			<instance src="jr://instance/casedb" id="casedb"/>
			<instance src="jr://instance/session" id="commcaresession"/>
			<bind vellum:nodeset="#form/confirm_remove" nodeset="/data/confirm_remove"/>
			<itext>
				<translation lang="en" default="">
					<text id="confirm_remove-label">
						<value>Swipe to remove the point at (<output value="instance('casedb')/casedb/case[@case_id = instance('commcaresession')/session/data/case_id]/x" vellum:value="#case/x"/>  ,<output value="instance('casedb')/casedb/case[@case_id = instance('commcaresession')/session/data/case_id]/y" vellum:value="#case/y"/>).</value>
					</text>
				</translation>
				<translation lang="fra">
					<text id="confirm_remove-label">
						<value>Swipe to remove the point at (<output value="instance('casedb')/casedb/case[@case_id = instance('commcaresession')/session/data/case_id]/x" vellum:value="#case/x"/>  ,<output value="instance('casedb')/casedb/case[@case_id = instance('commcaresession')/session/data/case_id]/y" vellum:value="#case/y"/>).</value>
					</text>
				</translation>
			</itext>
		</model>
		<vellum:hashtags>{"#case/x":null,"#case/y":null}</vellum:hashtags>
		<vellum:hashtagTransforms>{"prefixes":{"#case/parent/":"instance('casedb')/casedb/case[@case_id = instance('casedb')/casedb/case[@case_id = instance('commcaresession')/session/data/case_id]/index/parent]/","#case/":"instance('casedb')/casedb/case[@case_id = instance('commcaresession')/session/data/case_id]/","#user/":"instance('casedb')/casedb/case[@case_type = 'commcare-user'][hq_user_id = instance('commcaresession')/session/context/userid]/"}}</vellum:hashtagTransforms>
	</h:head>
	<h:body>
		<trigger vellum:ref="#form/confirm_remove" ref="/data/confirm_remove" appearance="minimal">
			<label ref="jr:itext('confirm_remove-label')"/>
		</trigger>
	</h:body>
</h:html>

<h:html xmlns:h="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:orx="http://openrosa.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2002/xforms" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:jr="http://openrosa.org/javarosa" xmlns:vellum="http://commcarehq.org/xforms/vellum">
	<h:head>
		<h:title>Add Point to Series</h:title>
		<model>
			<instance>
				<data xmlns:jrm="http://dev.commcarehq.org/jr/xforms" xmlns="http://openrosa.org/formdesigner/D7C7DFD6-919C-41DD-B709-A14CCEDE1972" uiVersion="1" version="1" name="Add Point to Series">
					<x/>
					<y/>
				</data>
			</instance>
			<bind vellum:nodeset="#form/x" nodeset="/data/x" type="xsd:int"/>
			<bind vellum:nodeset="#form/y" nodeset="/data/y" type="xsd:int"/>
			<itext>
				<translation lang="en" default="">
					<text id="x-label">
						<value>x</value>
					</text>
					<text id="y-label">
						<value>y</value>
					</text>
				</translation>
				<translation lang="fra">
					<text id="x-label">
						<value>x</value>
					</text>
					<text id="y-label">
						<value>y</value>
					</text>
				</translation>
			</itext>
		</model>
	</h:head>
	<h:body>
		<input vellum:ref="#form/x" ref="/data/x">
			<label ref="jr:itext('x-label')"/>
		</input>
		<input vellum:ref="#form/y" ref="/data/y">
			<label ref="jr:itext('y-label')"/>
		</input>
	</h:body>
</h:html>
